  • Interface Summary

    SystemProperties  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BooleanResult
    Wrapper class for a boolean value which may be referenced and modified.
    CRC_32
    CRC_32 is an Adler32 class extended by functionality to update the checksum under various parameter types.
    CRC_OutputStream
    Class to reflect data which is sent to this output stream into a CRC_32 checksum value.
    CRC64  
    DirectByteOutputStream
    Memory based output stream extending java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream in order to make available the accumulated data buffer in direct access.
    HashMac
    This abstract class implements the MD4-like block/padding structure as it is used by most hashes (MD4, MD5, SHA-0, SHA-1, RIPEMD-128, RIPEMD-160, Tiger).
    IntResult
    Wrapper class for a integer value (int) which may be referenced and modified.
    Log
    Log in org.jpws.pwslib.global Protocol, log and debug printing class.
    PropertySupport  
    SHA256  
    StringPair

    Util
